text: Neel van der Elst also known as Etna Vesuvia (17 September 1956 â€“ 8 January 2025) was a Dutch singer. Van der Elst was the singer of the former new wave music band from Amsterdam. Later she played in Etna Vesuvia & the Flames, Zinn Zinn et la Zizanie and in . She gained fame as Etna Vesuvia in the VPRO radio program Ronflonflon on Hilversum 3.
